* employee strikes are purposeful attacks on the employer, potentially collaterally hurting its customers too
* it is okay to change mind, to leave the employer if found unsatisfactory; but it is not okay to purposefully hurt the employer
* a job is a voluntary business relationship between 2 persons, the employee and the employer; similar to marriage; it is okay to change heart and divorce, but it is not okay to hurt the partner because he|she did not prove to be so nice as was hoped
